class.comment: The default implementation of WorldVersion that automatically detects the protocl and server version.

id.comment: The Unique Identifier of this Server's Version, as a trimmed UUID string.

name.comment: The Friendly Name of this Server's Version, such as "1.20.2".

stable.comment: Whether or not this Server's Version is considered stable.

worldVersion.comment: The WorldVersion of this Server's Version.

protocolVersion.comment: The Protocol Version of this Server's Version.

resourcePackVersion.comment: The Resource Pack Version ID of this Server's Version.

dataPackVersion.comment: The Data Pack Version ID of this Server's Version.

buildTime.comment: The Build Time of this Server's Version.

constructors.comment: Constructs a new DetectedVersion using hard-coded parameters.

params.name: json
params.comment: The JSON Object to read from.

constructors.comment: Constructs a new DetectedVersion using the given JSON Object. The inputted object is directly read from version.json, a file stored in the server JAR.

return.comment: The detected version, or the built-in version if the version cannot be detected.

tryDetectVersion.comment: Attempts to detect the version of the server. If the version cannot be detected, the built-in version is returned.
